  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3472751">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3472751/" class="title-link">自由、民主与政治权威</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3472751"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2409661/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2409661-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2409661/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">wayne</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-07-25"
      class="main-meta">2010-07-25 22:37:43</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3472751_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   《政治哲学与幸福根基》是David Miller写的一本牛津通识读物。大家的风范就在于举重若轻的气度，能在只言片语中将深奥的道理说透，本书将政治权威、民主、自由与正义的理论阐述得十分精彩，令人佩服。  现代社会是以国家的形式领导社会生活，政治权威在其中扮演着重要角色。那...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3472751/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">20有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3472751_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3472751_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8544363">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8544363/" class="title-link">领导叫我写点东西，可我就是不想写！不想写！不...</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8544363"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

