            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="18975084">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">民族是由对祖先的错觉和对邻居的惯常仇恨结合而成的社会。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-06-14 23:34</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>民族是由对祖先的错觉和对邻居的惯常仇恨结合而成的社会。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
